Description:
    Generates custom landing pages. Two main options of a simple setup with a url structure of *.com/pages/:page or a full setup *.com/:page

Example:
    rails generate landing_page account

    This will create:
        app/views/landing_pages/account.haml
        app/assets/stylesheets/account.sass
        add a line to routes
        add a line to landing_pages controller

    rails generate landing_page account --no-full --no-stylesheet

    This will create:
        app/views/landing_pages/account.haml
